These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
House: gothic-revival, palace
2 different games are played: canasta, billiard
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the palace house is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea     | hot-chocolate |
| House   | palace | gothic-revival      |
| Game         | billiard    | canasta      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, surfing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, salsa
2 different pets are kept: fish, goat
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the fan of punk##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |
| Sport         | surfing      | sailing |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | punk    |
| Pet           | goat         | fish         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-3::.
There 2 different types of food: peas, cabbage
2 different pets are kept: mouse, pony
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, mauve
1. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person eating peas is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2      |
| Food         | peas | cabbage |
| Pet         | pony       | mouse       |
| Color   | mauve       | fuchsia         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  mechanic, electrician
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, gardening
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Job    | electrician    | mechanic     |
| Hobby       | camping    | gardening |
| Sport   | swimming | skateboarding    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, davidoff
There 2 different types of food: orange, artichoke
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person eating artichoke is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person eating orange is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Cigar       | davidoff | oliveros |
| Food         | orange      | artichoke  |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-6::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, singing
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, swisher
City: new-york, london
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |
| Hobby   | singing   | hiking     |
| Cigar     | swisher | fonseca    |
| City   | london    | new-york |

