.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-15::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, accountant
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, r&b
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold
1. the bartender is on the far right##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Job         | accountant | bartender |
| Music-Genre   | r&b         | d&b       |
| Flower     | bellflower   | marigold       |

