.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, july
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, green
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse
1. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Birthday   | february | july   |
| Color   | green          | ivory   |
| Sport         | climbing     | lacrosse |

 